The playtesters domain is officially closed for applications, however applications from clerics, mages and thieves may still be considered.  If you wish to apply, please mudmail Shiannar answering the following questions.

1) Describe in less than 100 words why you should be a playtester on Divided Sky.

2) Which parts of the mud are you most interested in seeing developed.

3) Please list _up to_ three other people who can vouch for you.  These three people can be either player or creator.  Please ensure you have their permission before citing their name.

4) (Optional) Please list any other muds you have played on.  Character names are un-neccesary.
